Pt.1 PR unboxings 

Unboxing this beautiful PR box from Gubb and it’s aesthetic goals! 🌸 From the cutest leaf hair clips (perfect for that effortless hair flip look 🌿), a pink quartz face roller that screams pamper time, a comfy headband for my skincare routine, a chic hairbrush for those good hair days, to the most unique toothbrush-shaped makeup brush that’s honestly a game changer! 💖

This box is literally filled with everyday beauty must-haves that make self-care a little more fun and fab! 🌷 Whether you’re a skincare girlie or a haircare lover, Gubb has something for everyone.

🌸 Product Highlights:
	•	Leaf Hair Clips: Adds that boho charm to your hair game.
	•	Quartz Roller: For the ultimate glow up—helps with puffiness and gives that cooling effect.
	•	Makeup Brush (Toothbrush Shape): The perfect tool for flawless blending.
	•	Headband: Ideal for masking or makeup prep.
	•	Hairbrush: Sleek and smooth hair, here I come!

🛍️ Gubb is killing it with beauty tools that are not only functional but also aesthetic. I’m totally obsessed with the vibe of this PR box and can’t wait to use everything in my daily routine!

💬 Let me know in the comments: Which product would you love to try first? Or is there a must-have from Gubb that I should get my hands on next?

📸 Follow for more aesthetic unboxings, beauty reviews, and relatable finds! Let’s build our self-care stash together! 💗
